---
// "Why now?" market-context band (EUDR / ICVCM / TNFD).
---

<section class="bg-forest-900 text-white">
  <div class="container-content py-16">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] md:items-center">
      <p class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold text-brand-blue md:text-4xl">Why now?</p>
      <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-forest-100">
        New regulations (<span class="font-semibold text-white">EUDR</span>), integrity standards
        (<span class="font-semibold text-white">ICVCM</span>), and disclosure frameworks
        (<span class="font-semibold text-white">TNFD</span>) are raising the bar for what counts as
        credible forest monitoring. Whether you are issuing carbon credits, proving supply-chain
        compliance, or reporting on nature-related risk, the days of coarse satellite estimates are
        ending. We provide the ecological depth and AI precision these standards demand.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
